task.summary: Sensible defaults for bound symbols in defs (Effect symbols of blocks) + more descriptive comments for alias hints + syms and family

Added fixed point and integers, fixed bug with CSE. Changed metadata collection from Array of Sets to Array of Maps. Sets either don't ensure single copies of each type of metadata, or make the equals method on Metadata useless for use in the rest of the compiler
Revised cake pattern for argon ops to XOps (common), XAPI (app), and XCore (compiler)
